{"tid":522783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"調查指日本男童長大後最想做「學者‧博士」　女童最想成為 ...","createTime":"2018-01-08T00:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T02:14:03.000Z","uid":90017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2475164f27c38b856fa5072ed30ee5456c3e6cc2","tid":522783,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T00:48:33.000Z","msg":"日本《朝日新聞》報道，第一生命保險公司昨日（5日）對外公布，以孩童為對象的「長大後想成為？」問卷調查結果。男孩第1名為「學者‧博士」，擠下受歡迎的足球選手與棒球選手，睽違15年奪下冠軍。女孩第1名則是「餐飲店人員」，連續21年蟬聯第1名。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，從2003年以後，男孩的第1名不是「棒球選手」就是「足球選手」，然而「學者‧博士」則是從2016年的第2名上升到第1名。修訂《學習指導要領》得以豐富理科的授課內容、日本人相繼獲得諾貝爾獎等，這些因素似乎都有產生影響。提到要成為「學者‧博士」的孩童表示：「想要找出能完全治癒癌症的方法」、「想要製作能一起玩的機器人」。<br />\n<br />\n女孩的第2名為「護士」，第3名為「托兒所‧幼稚園老師」。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n此調查在2017年7月至9月進行，由第一生命的業務負責人詢問就讀國小6年級或以下的1100名孩童。<br />\n<br />\n★長大後想成為？<br />\n<br />\n〈男孩〉<br />\n1 (2) 學者‧博士<br />\n2 (4) 棒球選手<br />\n3 (1) 足球選手<br />\n4 (3) 警察‧刑警<br />\n4 (5) 醫生<br />\n<br />\n〈女孩〉<br />\n1 (1) 餐飲店人員<br />\n2 (4) 護士<br />\n3 (2) 托兒所‧幼稚園老師<br />\n4 (4) 醫生<br />\n5 (3) 學校老師(才藝老師)<br />\n<br />\n第1排數字為本次排名，括號內數字為2016年的排名。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/調查指日本男童長大後最想做-學者-博士-女童最想成為/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%8C%87%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E9%95%B7%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%80%E6%83%B3%E5%81%9A-%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85-%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB-%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E6%9C%80%E6%83%B3%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%2F&d=Pr%2FuIvySmj0k7xyqB7RJD54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=dbd7693e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%8C%87%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E9%95%B7%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%80%E6%83%B3%E5%81%9A-%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85-%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB-%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E6%9C%80%E6%83%B3%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%2F&h=fb4fca3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/調查指日本男童長大後最想做-學者-博士-女童最想成為/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3bd70aa8af2b5f39d723e18ba9fae257b98e9e","tid":522783,"uid":93900,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T00:50:37.000Z","msg":"餐飲店人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf035d7991672d820b4939372d865fc65fe41e2a","tid":522783,"uid":72498,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T00:52:11.000Z","msg":"以為女優<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94195866e5080e9869ecc351099103ff7a113ec0","tid":522783,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf035d7991672d820b4939372d865fc65fe41e2a","tid":522783,"uid":72498,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T00:52:11.000Z","msg":"以為女優<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T00:53:18.000Z","msg":"你估講緊香港啲濕鳩侍應咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f39b1bca1fa8f1a75e7060e456bd9c2743a2933","tid":522783,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T00:53:20.000Z","msg":"女仔果表，轉最正AV角色都得"},{"pid":"e718e9ef98eea861d454629fcb1d02d60bcc8e4c","tid":522783,"uid":103317,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T01:18:55.000Z","msg":"拍av就可以一次滿足你咁多個願望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5fb8e8f28b236771e6da82bde05241ad4fc4d1","tid":522783,"uid":90017,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T01:21:59.000Z","msg":"你班仆街剩係講av <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4313dc6c1b8c622f4314a4aa936aba412c97ca6","tid":522783,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e718e9ef98eea861